title: Ted Nugent: " I don't understand how Schimp can get to human rights. "
subtitle: Ted Nugent recently made comments about President Obama's support for the national football player of Colin Kaybernik's protests, but he did not call the athlete "a transvestite."
author: Kim LaCapria
vclaim: Ted Nugent called Colin Kaybernik Chimp when discussing the president's support for the sports protest.
